{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we had to operate on them, but when we operated on these SS doctors, the [INAUDIBLE] the [INAUDIBLE] doctor, who was a surgeon himself, he was operating with the two Polish doctors, together, because they would not trust, you know, just the Poles to operate on them, you know.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and I was doing the rest of the, you know, sterilizing, getting the instruments ready, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after that, for about a week or two, they were bringing SS people, you know, to our hospital, and we had to give them preference over anybody else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the way things went on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I remember other operations when people had very bad gangrene set in, in, in their legs, because you know, you have to understand, people were afraid to come to the hospital, because they knew, if you come to the hospital with a serious thing, and-- you never get out.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there are many people that had very bad injuries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, many people had very bad injuries on the back of their legs from the bad-- these clogs, the wooden clogs, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had very bad infections and gangrene, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember many times, you know, when they had to be amputated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I took these limbs into the next block, where they were doing experiments, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that's where Dr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mengele was operating, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to take some of these limbs into the next block and just drop them into a vat, you know, and there were other things floating in there, you know, all kinds of body parts, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What kinds of things did you see in, in this other block?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
